        <title>MyBatis-Plus 逻辑删除与唯一索引冲突问题解决方案</title>
        <link>https://XingSea.github.io/p/mybatis-plus-%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%8E%E5%94%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</link>
